title: Travis - Fred Duval and Christophe Quet (English)
description:
Travis is set in the near future of 2052, society is dominated by multinationals. While Steve Travis, a freelance pilot, is making a simple delivery to an orbital space station he finds himself caught in the middle of a conflict between two firms specializing in agronomy and biotechnology.

Written by Fred Duval with art by Christophe Quet.

This torrent contains the first four volumes translated into English
